          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="feat__ico"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="instagram" size="21"></svg></div>
          <h3 data-v-16d9afef="">Auto-import photos</h3>
          <p data-v-16d9afef=""> Connect your camera roll and Instagram — geotagged shots flow straight onto the right place on the map. </p>
