          <h3 data-v-16d9afef="">Write it</h3>
          <p data-v-16d9afef=""> Add a note, a rating, the hidden detail you'll want to remember — or the reason you'd send a friend. </p>
        </div>
        <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="step">
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="step__n">STEP 03</div>
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="step__ico"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="globe" size="22"></svg></div>
