  <section data-v-16d9afef="" id="journal" class="lp-sec">
    <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="lp">
      <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="sec-head" data-reveal="">
        <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="label">// 05 — the journal</div>
        <h2 data-v-16d9afef="">Your travels, <b data-v-16d9afef="">beautifully kept.</b></h2>
        <p data-v-16d9afef=""> Every entry is a small, lovely record — location, photos, the words you wrote that day. The opposite of a thousand un-labelled photos in a camera roll. </p>
      </div>
      <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="entries3" data-reveal-stagger="" data-reveal-step="100">
        <article data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3">
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__img ph">
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="topo" style="opacity: 0.4;"></div>
          </div>
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__b">
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__loc"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="pin" size="11"></svg> Reykjavík, IS </div>
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__t">Harbor at 4am</div>
            <p data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__x"> Cold morning, the whole harbor still asleep. Found coffee at a window and watched the boats. </p>
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__f"><span data-v-16d9afef=""><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="calendar" size="13"></svg> Jun 12</span><span data-v-16d9afef=""><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="image" size="13"></svg> 6 photos</span><span data-v-16d9afef=""><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="heart" size="13"></svg> 24</span></div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3">
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__img ph">
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="topo" style="opacity: 0.4;"></div>
          </div>
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__b">
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__loc"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="pin" size="11"></svg> Lisbon, PT </div>
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__t">Tram 28, again</div>
            <p data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__x"> Took the long way through Alfama. Pastéis de nata, then a viewpoint I keep coming back to. </p>
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__f"><span data-v-16d9afef=""><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="calendar" size="13"></svg> Jun 8</span><span data-v-16d9afef=""><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="image" size="13"></svg> 12 photos</span><span data-v-16d9afef=""><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="heart" size="13"></svg> 41</span></div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3">
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__img ph">
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="topo" style="opacity: 0.4;"></div>
          </div>
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__b">
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__loc"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="pin" size="11"></svg> Tokyo, JP </div>
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__t">Last train from Shinjuku</div>
            <p data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__x"> Neon and rain on the platform. Ramen at a counter that sat six. Wrote this on the ride home. </p>
            <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="e3__f"><span data-v-16d9afef=""><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="calendar" size="13"></svg> May 30</span><span data-v-16d9afef=""><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="image" size="13"></svg> 9 photos</span><span data-v-16d9afef=""><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="heart" size="13"></svg> 63</span></div>
          </div>
        </article>
