  </section><!-- ============ TESTIMONIALS ============ -->
  <section data-v-16d9afef="" id="loved" class="lp-sec lp-sec--tint">
    <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="lp">
      <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="sec-head center" data-reveal="">
        <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="label">// 06 — loved by travelers</div>
        <h2 data-v-16d9afef="">The home base for <b data-v-16d9afef="">people without one.</b></h2>
      </div>
      <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="quotes" data-reveal-stagger="" data-reveal-step="100">
        <figure data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote">
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__stars"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg></div>
          <p data-v-16d9afef=""> "I've lived out of a backpack for two years across eleven countries. Wanderist is the only record of it that I actually trust — and the only one I reread." </p>
          <figcaption data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__who"><span data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__av"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="user" size="18"></svg></span><span data-v-16d9afef=""><span data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__name">Maya R.</span><br data-v-16d9afef=""><span data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__role">Product designer · remote</span></span></figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote">
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__stars"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg></div>
          <p data-v-16d9afef=""> "The photo import is magic. I land somewhere new and by the evening my whole day is already pinned and dated. No more mystery camera rolls." </p>
          <figcaption data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__who"><span data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__av"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="user" size="18"></svg></span><span data-v-16d9afef=""><span data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__name">Diego S.</span><br data-v-16d9afef=""><span data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__role">Software engineer · digital nomad</span></span></figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote">
          <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__stars"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="star" size="15"></svg></div>
          <p data-v-16d9afef=""> "Discover sends me to the places friends-of-friends loved, not the top ten lists. I've found my favorite cafés in three cities this way." </p>
          <figcaption data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__who"><span data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__av"><svg data-v-16d9afef="" data-icon="" name="user" size="18"></svg></span><span data-v-16d9afef=""><span data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__name">Priya K.</span><br data-v-16d9afef=""><span data-v-16d9afef="" class="quote__role">Writer · slow traveler</span></span></figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section><!-- ============ PRICING TEASER ============ -->
  <section data-v-16d9afef="" id="plans" class="lp-sec">
    <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="lp">
      <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="sec-head center" data-reveal="">
        <div data-v-16d9afef="" class="label">// 07 — plans</div>
        <h2 data-v-16d9afef="">Start free. <b data-v-16d9afef="">Go further when you do.</b></h2>
        <p data-v-16d9afef=""> Every plan keeps your map and journal forever. Upgrade only when you're traveling enough to need more. </p>
      </div>
